    "phase_0_projection": "You are producing an English caption for a symbolic-music segment.\n\nEvidence policy:\n- Realize only claims listed under `caption_projection.allowed_claims`.\n- Do not verbalize any item under `caption_projection.blocked_claims`.\n- Match each claim's `assertion_level`; use centered or suggestive wording when required.\n- State an exact sequence or trend only when its evidence value is explicit.\n- Return one raw JSON object with `caption_short`, `caption_detailed`, and short claim-to-evidence links.\n\nInput modalities:\n{{input_modalities}}\n\nCaption projection:\n{{caption_projection}}",
    "pilot_supported_evidence": "You are producing an English music caption for a symbolic MIDI segment.\n\nEvidence policy:\n- Use only fields under `metadata.supported_evidence` whose status is `supported`.\n- Treat `metadata.uncertain_or_unknown_evidence` as blocked attributes.\n- State a pitch sequence, rhythm, contour, or trend only when explicit symbolic evidence is supplied.\n- Return one raw JSON object with short and detailed captions plus evidence paths.\n\nInput evidence:\n{{metadata}}"
  },
